==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: colonized
<hw>colonized</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>inhabited by people
who were born in or retain strong ties to another country.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> settled.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>politically ruled by citizens of another
country.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>having a population (of animals or plants) which
moved in from another territory.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> colonized.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colonizer</ent>⟦br⟧
